l style="padding-left: 10px; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;流媒体视频公司 Netflix 宣布，在其首次大型直播体育赛事和《Squid Game》回归的推动下，2024 年&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=8416ac90d8964be69432d2ab2304f259&amp;amp;_e=MgJXxQ7Vlx5rLlC4E-lsoZU5hCYCc2gRczVxnTsf_48LOhQ33OfLtsv4B8vHq7etTZ7gmmKdKgTq9OVnPj8jLgYrGN_b0ugofOYcRVoAsTA5_xXjUmCxUgqxuIzX5oHopoEZsSPXTHSnbjsRk6qnZKWLzJKHeYJ_6v0lUP1dn8QB0vLCTwp4PZ7koJNu4PzLXEPc7ulpYAbrHfgE-j96X2ZSIrwQU7GRszfqgzf8CSqxCnkKIjSrlFgqMS2YL1Vx8poTKO3apbQwvjh89TvkkSTGLgLB23bMJ7WWjaOTu7nR9c3nTZSxUTr5XDDaWlMRqD63G2TNY3LgupNwol_Huw%3D%3D" target="_blank" title="关联"&gt;的订阅用户增幅创下历史最高&lt;/a&gt;纪录，该公司盘前股价飙升 15% &lt;em&gt;。&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;美国总统唐纳德·特朗普表示，他对中国商品征收 10% 关税的威胁仍在考虑之中，可能会在下个月实施，随后&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=8416ac90d8964be69432d2ab2304f259&amp;amp;_e=MgJXxQ7Vlx5rLlC4E-lsoaH2xMqA5rGpVJk6hOnesWp7aVqf4JIiLUKGwF80mBpLOFa38SWik9ZCQH8W9WBrklZTndPvxmLeEQ2Wt7GUwA4GeOT5hlNqffB0GteayD5n1V65APR7JPJOemXmBct91TS9rPpCME_rm6Q0o3_1lRLWGbJYzx73tqefgC06Bo8waAMW0SMLNnb9l0KcXocDtxGL2noR9P971SRY0WGwrZKMVGRRkYH9cluSUC3g9kVGR1gpe13r7ackEWzGfmdsx09tGevx5wJZgutikvl50fkTRPxoxdUd4lpHoLrEZ4J6O0EEgI_0nJ2YwdRUEcLXJA%3D%3D" target="_blank" title="关联"&gt;中国股市错过了&lt;/a&gt;涨势。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;特朗普将对埃隆·马斯克或甲骨文公司的拉里·埃里森&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=8416ac90d8964be69432d2ab2304f259&amp;amp;_e=MgJXxQ7Vlx5rLlC4E-lsoe9-d1Jlsc5MxhXIs6eDLLayPSDjs78MVVW4m6auSWuCk-dM1BS35FWe0LpSOAVMNZp03BLpUdgQlfXzP8DMuAETFwRbcbh-iest2smf6OYzAG_WF8QdvTVP331Q5UJXSQ7JrtjLLndqSH6x6A9extqfUb9cC9UraV4vekyuA4qVS0OX3WU1OeUQQJXdM4AebT6fuuoUNx52RmxTr3LvvE_5ZGZ7S97N1N0i7E7jHuv2r7dUChNkoWjEea-myzIpimWPLKX4XzPuhxZHPu1o5FztLLnoha4tvSCtssEULIjqB95WyBrb58iAvfEZd6vOaA%3D%3D" target="_blank" title="关联"&gt;与美国政府合作&lt;/a&gt;购买 TikTok 持开放态度。 “所以我想对某人说的是买下它，一半给美利坚合众国，一半，我们会给你许可证，他们将有一个伟大的合作伙伴，”他说。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;软银、OpenAI 和甲骨文正在组建一家&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=8416ac90d8964be69432d2ab2304f259&amp;amp;_e=MgJXxQ7Vlx5rLlC4E-lsoTywnx-EAh9l33CYPamzf_6ebSAkddkTes_JwASIKOwkPnCRuA-HRbk8qmeZYo8tVStGUXentUMMHJWmDYyCnqfjk3c-ceC3PA6QppLv7fLiYlaWWMLiJm51EWqRsf3Aw8bVhZZz-v1thlCWK80BAPmWcB3k5wAI-GUG4r4va6bRsOjxNQK9SWF3V4_y2xFXjwFg6a539lS6KGduxl2aPGg-ROq0hoqgv3da4M_wHhcNIf3Ow-OG-hs5Z9lEGqJGnPAy7heUtfwyrO9mdXpXpB2TUpVBhPVGX1vQc6_ZVpW4iKf3So56cFMbhl3eXS0gmQ%3D%3D" target="_blank" title="关联"&gt;1000 亿美元的合资企业&lt;/a&gt;，为人工智能基础设施提供资金，特朗普与特朗普共同宣布了这一举措，旨在&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=8416ac90d8964be69432d2ab2304f259&amp;amp;_e=MgJXxQ7Vlx5rLlC4E-lsoSWseyPR97QxyQEioqiOmQoXUXAyXJMq98RxBnsXensbypjmcayY7BzJepOHZ8ujbK9W7SUVYBRy50P0_5EB9xOyu66LwxDNbB3x03zW37nWuqEXUAbXtub2JTaTTPj1amR8Ze_NSgzcwUFMZeiidI8Z92gJBI2KEI0ptPZ609LOAElCiMdbaGmRKtguUJfDE0A1mCbORuGFBfovADBIITYWxD6doyPAQTQ7YxRahnYGZr9_w37hLDx1EzTNx0TEMREyVAs1X7IFhQzhBp7vIylA_MHdgL8BXjxh0JU_WR-OL17HHveT5zF1eEHezwA6pg%3D%3D" target="_blank" title="关联"&gt;加速该技术的发展&lt;/a&gt;。盘前交易中， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=8416ac90d8964be69432d2ab2304f259&amp;amp;_e=MgJXxQ7Vlx5rLlC4E-lsocEerLrNPnXKxZlEHCeN1rPb5HfVXNhnTP24KQjuDJnIe3L6ZdC8-69_W_BbwkkVUQWhvIQIHHTv17vWPG2_PEBJtZmuf3hHxG0JMpyScBtLVTwYqO5LkSfeZuTTC5o9AjeqNBR2VIjudEMluYAMoV9otfXQ2Z0RmkXGPtVF8nYrUOjp_xwVKc-nQawuARp314K5mFJk0vJXKifGVcmp6VnnbVZ-DHRpXEYvG7-aO03B6AmDkgEwTXfge8Z1qgbb1NKfxFxcOTkeY03BAkOmsnOQLborgr3ePOXGwRB8ThkqyCc8OiiCUmN86dpyQGbMlw%3D%3D" target="_blank" title="关联"&gt;软银股价飙升&lt;/a&gt;11%，甲骨文股价上涨 10%。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;人工智能计划正在帮助提振美国&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t